data.description: MOVE IN READY!  BIG PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  MOTIVATED SELLERS. NEW HVAC Aug 1-$14k.  Sellers offering $20k credit at closing for repair of driveway. Mid Century Modern, w updated open floor plan.  Great for entertaining, Chandlers Landing gated community. On-site HOA,  2 community pools, 2 tennis courts, 4 catch & release ponds, playgrounds, basketball courts, walking trails, greenbelts, 24 hr scrty & patrol, & community center.  Gated entry to home enters beautiful private courtyard. Saltillo tile &, LVP,  No carpet.  Exposed wood ceiling, & many architectural features w open floor plan. Updated oversized primary shower!!  Tons of natural light! Lrge kitchen island w beautiful backsplash, stone & butcher block counter tops, & more!  Wet bar open to dining & living room.  Primary bedroom overlooks the courtyard & has a beautiful luxury bath..  Secondary bdrms share jack & jill bath. Resort style backyard with POOL!  New survey needed.
